high_descs: Turn right, walk to the round table in the corner, turn right walk to the white table.
Pick up the cup and the spoon under the cup on the table.
Turn around then turn left and walk towards the stove.
Put the cup with the spoon under it on the counter to the left of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put the cup and the spoon on the counter.

high_descs: Turn to the right and then the right again to find the white table.
Pick up the cup from the back of the white table.
Hold the cup and turn around, then left to find the stove.
Place the cup on the counter to the left of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Move a cup to the counter.

high_descs: Turn right, walk to the black table, then turn right again and go to the white table.
Pick up the small black pot.
Turn around and then approach the stove on your left.
Put the pot on the counter between the stove and the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put the pot from the table on the counter between the stove and the fridge.
